response.overview: On November 21, 2017, Aimesse Yamanashi in Kofu, Yamanashi, Japan hosted Day 4 of NJPW World Tag League 2017, broadcast on [station].  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Kazuchika Okada, Tomohiro Ishii & Toru Yano).  The card also featured War Machine (Hanson & Raymond Rowe) vs Suzuki-gun (El Desperado, Minoru Suzuki, Takashi Iizuka & Yoshinobu Kanemaru).  Other wrestlers on the show include TenKoji (Hiroyoshi Tenzan & Satoshi Kojima), Ren Naritavs and Shota Umino, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 4
